0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:45:53.000Z","msg":"綜合黎講公主光美真係屈晒機，無論係作畫劇情節奏演出全部都極高水準，某幾集直頭有劇場版級作畫，完全想像唔到係幼女向作品黎睇到O晒嘴，出D招全部有唔同效果唔係鳩打，單體攻擊範圍技反擊控場乜都有，仲可以兩招合埋變組合技真係磁能線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過個人最鍾意星光光美，雖然整體有D鳩流但某幾集同後期勁正（一齊幫架火箭油油<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），睇完劇場版再聽住Twinkle Stars睇返最尾2集喊到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0072e5215bcaed22bf61a177bd8a09226c5e8ac7","tid":2468210,"uid":39181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:52:25.000Z","msg":"最鍾意呢代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWjRz5Gwu7xBLzHW1quxTKr31b4m1e9pj7nwuM6Uoj2aW?filename=tj92o0j.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftj92o0j.gif&h=4d7368a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9dbd0cee2c4f3d8b2696fb219e5fbf52e9c2799d","tid":2468210,"uid":39181,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:53:32.000Z","msg":"綠毛外星人都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeuEWgvdxSH1k5brneJPZo5aioNp6LKBHwrzbsEKTJTYf?filename=cG9axTW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcG9axTW.png&h=9578eb63&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"462ad553744f496f4c475a70b8bb34dfe0f9bd3e","tid":2468210,"uid":209662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9faa51d0488bd6dd523ab5d0a8224132e4b66f62","tid":2468210,"uid":252993,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-30T11:19:31.000Z","msg":"比較鍾意光豬美少女<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:59:40.000Z","msg":"光洙美少男呢？？"},{"pid":"3c54346aa05bceb842e5e1319c03362ed13867c6","tid":246821